| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7480 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1efc777a-9fb7-5eda-b0dc-6de5aa9615d8"
